{"tid":1823761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首稱單程證是為家庭團聚　是人權和自由   改動政策不是考慮方案","createTime":"2020-01-14T03:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T11:17:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b0705129d76e4c5b23abd7ec4862eed7c1d50fff","tid":1823761,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"廣東省政協常委、新地執行董事郭基煇在廣東省政協十二屆三次會議上，提出把單程證上限由每日150個削減至75個。行政長官林鄭月娥被問到是否有可能做到這個建議，以及這個建議是否能達到紓緩中港兩地之間的誤解。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，單程證政策是為了家庭團聚，必須尊重讓家庭可以一同生活，這是人權和自由。她說，在這個時候改動政策或名額會帶出訊息，會將某一社會現象，推向家庭團聚的政策，這個不是政府考慮中的方案。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，現時單程證名額仍是150個是按政策和需要，由內地機關審批，而過去兩年沒有用盡，因為不想造成現象，有太多人利用這個制度來港定居。現時配偶分隔兩地的個案仍要輪候4年，現時有3分1屬跨境婚姻。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502661-20200114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502661-20200114.htm&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=51080326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502661-20200114.htm&h=bef6dd6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502661-20200114.htm</a>"},{"pid":"38d72345d92251a0c40eb07c17f75c15cb5a69b7","tid":1823761,"uid":5637,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"死上去大灣區團聚啦，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cca8deb53a6fec75c49b657a78c9693e2049de","tid":1823761,"uid":184679,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/962bd40735fae6cdac499e3c03b30f2443a70fe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F7Po3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F962bd40735fae6cdac499e3c03b30f2443a70fe9.jpg&h=9a82adba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e82b970ac14249595